dct_title_s: Lämpliga färdvägar för tung trafik inom Stockholm 1968-1969
dct_description_sm: AB Kartografiska Institutet. Generalstabens Litografiska Anstalt. [Suitable routes for heavy traffic within Stockholm 1968-69]. "Komplement till Kungörelse angående Lokala trakföreskrifterna inom Stockholm gällande per 1 april 1968." 34 routes for heavy traffic detailed on margin. Excerpts of relevant traffic regulations on bottom margin.
